data.description: Welcome to this lovely 4 bedroom, 2.5 bathroom colonial situated in the sought-after Valley Creek Estates neighborhood. This home boasts a spacious layout and plenty of natural light throughout. As you enter, you'll find a versatile formal dining room that can easily serve as a cozy sitting area, home office, or a play space for the kids. The family room flows seamlessly into the well-appointed eat-in kitchen, featuring ample cabinet space, updated flooring, and stainless steel appliances that are sure to impress. Next to the kitchen is an amazing morning room, perfect for everyday meals and gatherings, with sliders leading to the newly added large composite deck. Take in the peaceful surroundings of the private backyard. Upstairs, the second floor offers a large master bedroom complete with a spacious walk-in closet and a full bathroom. Three additional bedrooms share another full bathroom, providing ample space for the whole family. The convenience of a second-floor laundry room makes laundry days a breeze. The full, walk-out basement is ready for your personal touch and comes with plumbing for an additional full bath. With fresh paint throughout most of the home and a recently replaced H2O tank, this home is move-in ready and waiting for your family to make it their own. With quick occupancy available, seize the opportunity to create lasting memories in this wonderful family home. Schedule a showing today and see for yourself the endless possibilities this amazing property has to offer!
